rows.label: tev000893_MSG0001
rows.name: Oh, it's you, [ST:playername ].[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0002
rows.name: Don't worry, I ain't been in any fights today. ...Yet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0003
rows.name:
Had the day off, so I figured I'd try my luck with the
ladies and see what happened.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Yelv how it went.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_JNK0020
rows.name: Intervene[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_SEL0021
rows.name: Stop Yelv from hitting on anyone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0009
rows.name:
It went terribly is how it went!
But I think I got an idea that'll help...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0010
rows.name:
I'm gonna draw my gun, maybe fire a few rounds into
the air. Chicks love that![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_JNK0110
rows.name: Intervene[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_SEL0111
rows.name: Say that firing a gun is illegal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_JNK0120
rows.name: Punch[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_SEL0121
rows.name: Stop Yelv by punching him in the face.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0016
rows.name: Yeah, I know that, genius! Sheesh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0018
rows.name:
Whoa there! Easy! Keep your fists down by your
goddamn sides where they belong.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0019
rows.name:
And don't deny that you're about to punch me.
It's written all over your face.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0021
rows.name:
Look, people do the gun thing all the time in the
movies, right? Guess I just wanted to be a badass.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0022
rows.name: Anyway, thanks for setting me straight.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0023
rows.name: This is all Eleonora's fault, anyway.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0024
rows.name:
She's the one who told me I should study up on Earth
culture. Even gave me a bunch of movies to watch.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0025
rows.name: Unfortunately, most of 'em were old gangster flicks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0026
rows.name:
It seemed like people walked around firing guns all the
time in the old LA, yeah? Guess I just took it a little
more to heart than I should have.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0027
rows.name: I'm gonna bitch at Eleonora right now![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0028
rows.name: I'll talk to ya some other time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0032
rows.name:
Yeah, it ain't been goin' well at all. I'd pretty much
decided to give up before you opened your mouth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0033
rows.name: This is all Eleonora's fault...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0034
rows.name:
She said, "Yelv, you need to get to know more people
besides me and [ST:playername ].[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0035
rows.name:
"Bring back a girl you don't already know,
and I'll double the pay on your next job!"[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0036
rows.name:
But now that I think about it, I doubt Eleonora even
gets to set our pay.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0037
rows.name: She was probably just using me to kill some time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0038
rows.name: Man, this whole thing was a goddamn waste.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000893_MSG0039
rows.name:
I'm gonna go sign up for an extermination mission to
clear my head. Carvin' up a few ciniculas ought to
make me right as rain.[ST:wait ]
